data.description: Escape to your own private mountain retreat! This secluded cabin, tucked up above Camp Nelson and Pierpoint Springs on five acres, gives you the best of both worlds - privacy and feeling like you are all by  yourself in the mountains but close enough to both communities to enjoy events and activities.  You enter this lovely cabin into the main floor great room where you can enjoy the magnificent views from the great room as well as from each of the two main floor bedrooms. Step out to the deck for even better views and access to the downstairs which also features a view deck (with a spa no less), as well as a bedroom/bonus room and a half bath. A garage offers convenience and a sun deck built on the hillside above the cabin offers even more spectacular views. Did I mention it has been updated with recent paint and light fixtures, a laundry closest with custom barn doors, and new floors and vanities in the upstairs baths? Call today!
